Clearly some at least of the symbols must have been employed concurrently. The striking with ram's head has been placed first since one of its
                  reverse dies has the symbol below Nike's wing; thereafter the symbol is centered in the left field. Two obverse dies link Series I and II;
                  there is one link between Series II and III. Thus far there seems to be an orderly progression of emissions with output on a modest scale.

